OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fclear spells in the evening, though
OL,7,Fbreezy. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight, with the odd spot of rain
OL,9,For drizzle possible, mainly over
OL,10,Fhigher ground where it will be windy.
OL,11,FFeeling cooler than recently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FRather cloudy, with sunny
OL,14,Fspells tentatively developing in the
OL,15,Feast but the odd light shower likely
OL,16,Fin the west. Generally cloudy
OL,17,Fovernight, with outbreaks of mostly
OL,18,Flight rain spreading eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
